<Layout title={`Page ${page} - Black Maternal Mortality`}>
	<h1>Page {page}</h1>

	{pageNumber === 1 && (
		<>
			<h2>All About Black Maternal Mortality:</h2>
			<div class="content">
				<h3>What is the Issue:</h3>
				<p>
					Black Maternal Mortality has been and still is a pressing issue in the United States today. 
				</p>
				<img src="/images/statpage1.png" alt={`statpage1`} class="float-img"/>
				<p>
					There are several black mothers who’ve undergone complications in their pregnancy (such as preeclampsia), but do not get the proper care they need. This is typically because of the discrimination they face when seeking healthcare for these issues (Chambers et. al) This can affect these mothers’ and infants’ health, and in some cases, lead to death- often solely due to their racial identity. Unfortunately, this is still a common occurrence in the United States, and we have not taken significant action to solve this issue.
				</p>
				<div class="quiz-calculator-container">
				<div>
				</div>
				<div class="quiz-section">
					<Quiz questions={
						[
							{
								question: "What is the median mortality rate of all ethnicities on the graph? ",
								options: ["2.27", "22.6", "33.1283"],
								correctAnswer: 1
							},
							{
								question: "Is the maternal mortality rate higher or lower than the median?",
								options: ["Higher", "Lower"],
								correctAnswer: 0
							},
						]
					} shortAnswerQuestions={empty} />
				</div>
				<div class="calculator-section">
					<h2>Desmos Calculator</h2>
					<p>Use this embedded Desmos calculator for your mathematical needs!</p>
					<div class="calculator-container">
						<iframe src="https://www.desmos.com/calculator/scientific" width="100%" height="500" style="border: 1px solid #ccc" frameborder="0"></iframe>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			</div>
		</>
	)}
	{pageNumber === 2 && (
		<>
			<h2>Choose a Celebrity to learn about!</h2>
			<div class="content">
				<table>
					<thead>
						<tr>
							<th>Name</th>
							<th>Link</th>
						</tr>
					</thead>
					<tbody>
						<tr>
							<td>Serena Williams</td>
							<td><a href="https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/tennis/2022/04/07/serena-williams-near-death-childbirth-complications/9504616002/#:~:text=I'm%20used%20to%20getting,And%20her%20pain%20increased.&text=Although%20the%20hospital%20staff%20didn,by%20experts%20to%20be%20preventable.%22" target="_blank">Serena Williams describes near-death experience she had after giving birth to daughter Olympia</a></td>
						</tr>
						<tr>
							<td>Tori Bowie</td>
							<td><a href="https://www.npr.org/2023/06/13/1181971448/tori-bowie-an-elite-olympic-athlete-died-of-complications-from-childbirth" target="_blank">Tori Bowie, an elite Olympic athlete, died of complications from childbirth</a></td>
						</tr>
						<tr>
							<td>Allyson Felix</td>
							<td><a href="https://www.cdc.gov/hearher/allyson-felix/index.html" target="_blank">Unexpected Pregnancy Complications: Allyson Felix's Story</a></td>
						</tr>
					</tbody>
				</table>
			</div>
		</>
	)}
	{pageNumber === 3 && (
		<>
			<h2>Learn about your Celebrity!</h2>
			<div class="quiz-section">
			<Quiz questions={empty} 
				shortAnswerQuestions={[
					{
						question: "What are 2 things you learned from reading these articles.",
					}]} />
			</div>
		</>
	)}
	{pageNumber === 4 && (
		<>
			<h2>Meet Aaliyah</h2>
			<div class="content">
				<h3> All about Aaliyah: </h3>
