				<p>
					Age: 28
					<br>
					Income: $70,000          
					<br>
					Weeks Pregnant: 24
					<br>
					This is her first pregnancy
					<br>
					She has her husband and mother as a support system
					<br>
					She grew up in a middle class family with her mom 
					<br>
					She's active and like to run and yoga
				</p>
			</div>
		</>
	)}
	{pageNumber === 5 && (
		<>
			<h2>Aaliyah talks to a white doctor.</h2>
			<div class="content">
