		<>
			<h2>Treatment options</h2>
			<p><i>Recommends early delivery for the baby</i></p>
			<p><i>Seizures, heart issues (cardiomyopathy), pulmonary edema, (baby – Growth restrictions, preterm birth, intrauterine death)</i></p>
			<p><i>Management → Anti-hypertensive meds (hydrolozine, ) anti-seizure meds (magnesium sulfate), preventative → baby aspirin. </i></p>
			<p><i>If black women don’t get diagnosed they a much higher maternal mortality rate. Other complications can be Seizures, Coma, Stroke → Can lead to serious health problems. </i></p>
		</>
	)}

