				<div class="quiz-section">
					<Quiz questions={
						[
							{
								question: "Which of these statements are NOT correct?",
								options: ["Black mothers are over twice as likely to undergo a stillbirth as white women.", "Black maternal mortality happens due to a lack of money to access healthcare.", "BOTH black mothers and their infants have a higher chance of mortality than white or hispanic mothers and infants. "],
