			<p>Further Info on the Issue: </p>
			<ul>
				<li>Reducing health inequities for Black pregnant people <a href="https://www.vcuhealth.org/news/reducing-health-inequities-for-black-pregnant-people/#:~:text=Initiatives%20include%20evaluating%20care%20practices%20for%20potential,bias%20so%20it%20doesn't%20impact%20our%20care" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Visit Website</a></li>
				<li>Why are Black maternal mortality rates so high? <a href="https://mcpress.mayoclinic.org/pregnancy/black-maternal-mortality-rate/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Learn More</a></li>
			</ul>
			<p>How to get involved: </p>
			<ul>
				<li>Join the <a href="https://blackmamasmatter.org/connect/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Black Mamas Matter Alliance</a></li>
				<li>Get involved in <a href="https://www.sistersong.net/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Sister Song</a></li>
			</ul>
		</>
	)}
	
